2Pong is a local co-op game

There are two players in 2Pong:

Player 1 (Orange) is located on the left hand side of the game window and is controlled using the following keys:
w: Moves Player1 vertically upward
z: Moves Player1 vertically downward

Player 2 (Green) is located on the right hand side of the game window and is controlled using the following keys:
UP ARROW KEY: Moves Player1 vertically upward
DOWN ARROW KEY: Moves Player1 vertically downward

The game continuosly runs and keeps track of player scores until the QUIT key/button is pressed 
